question:
What will be the output of the following code?

```java
class Box {
    int width;
    Box(int w) { width = w; }
}

class Test {
    static Box modify(Box b) {
        b.width *= 2;
        return b;
    }
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Box b1 = new Box(5);
        Box b2 = modify(b1);
        System.out.print(b1.width + " " + b2.width);
    }
}
```

